quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,56,"Uchimwene lyele lisikulyo uchiŵa wa Allah pe, Jwalakwe tachijilanya chilikati chao. Basi aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, takaŵe m’Matimbe Gachindimba (ku Mbepo)"
  22,57,"Sano aŵala ŵakufuulu ni kaanila ma Ȃya Getu, basi ŵanganyao akwete kupata ilagasyo yakwalusya"
  22,58,"Sano aŵala ŵaŵasamile petala lya Allah, kaneko ni kuulajidwa kapena kuwa, chisimu Allah tachapa lisiki lyambone, soni chisimu Allah ni jwaali Jwambone nnope mwa akupeleka lisiki"
  22,59,"Chisimu ŵanganyao tachajinjisya pakwinjila patachipanonyela (ku Mbepo). Soni chisimu Allah ni Jwakumanyilila kusyesyene, Jwakutulala nnope ntima"
  22,60,"Yalakweyo ili iyyo. Sano juchauchisye ni ipotesi yakulandana ni ayila yajwapedwile jwalakwe kaneko ni kutendeledwa uwwanga, chisimu Allah tankamuchisye. Chisimu Allah ni Nkusiimaasya (ilemwa), Jwakuluka kusyene"
  22,61,"Yalakweyo ni ligongo lyanti Allah akwinjisyaga chilo m’muusi (ni kuleupa muusi kwipipa chilo mpela ndaŵi jachitukuta), ni akwinjisyaga soni muusi nchilo (ni kuleupa chilo kwipipa muusi mpela ndaŵi jakusisima), soni ligongo lyanti Allah ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakulolechesya"
  22,62,"Yalakweyo ni ligongo lyanti Allah ni jwali Jwakuona, soni kuti ayila yaakuiŵendaga yangaŵaga Jwalakwe ni yaili yaukoleko, soni kuti Allah ni jwali Jwapenani kusyene, Jwankulungwa kwannope"
  22,63,"Ana ngankuiona yanti Allah akutulusyaga kuumila kwinani mesi (gawula), basi litaka ni likasasyuka kuŵa lyakubiliŵitala? Chisimu Allah ni Jwakumanyilila yakunyilila nnope, Jwaasimanya abali syosope"
  22,64,"Iŵele Yakwe yosope yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka. Soni chisimu Allah ni Jwakupata kwejinji, Jwakulapilidwa kusyesyene"